<subSubSection id="760B07E2B648F5B9BBEDD7D0AEC6FA05" pageId="null" pageNumber="829" type="vernacular_names">
<paragraph id="802CBDDF52C904C1F7BBB008163DDBBA" pageId="null" pageNumber="829">Pfriemen-Mastkraut</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="38623DB51D5C97ABAC4EBA078CD16BBA" pageId="null" pageNumber="829" type="description">
<paragraph id="A3F573225E6ED8860D6924B3024CD9BF" pageId="null" pageNumber="829">
Unterscheidet sich von 
<taxonomicName id="27D1E6E7FE0D2C7E8DA2FB5A31E1C19A" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Caryophyllaceae" genus="Sagina" kingdom="Plantae" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="null" pageNumber="829" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="linnaei">
<emphasis id="7BCBF98A1118A6C116B2D25AACD18B02" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="829">S. Linnaei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 3) durch folgende Merkmale: 
<emphasis id="129BE80DF70AA41A835A6CB6C4E349AE" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="829">
Pflanze zerstreut, kurz und 
<normalizedToken id="52215E1E451386788728B21565001607" originalValue="drüsig" pageId="null" pageNumber="829">druesig</normalizedToken>
behaart;
</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="02F3A343D87E7BDAAFB3FB049792CF11" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="829">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
10-40mal so lang wie breit. 
<emphasis id="914EC307EF9F78425202EF661381F64F" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="829">Blattspitze 0,4-0,5 mm lang, etwa so lang wie die Blattbreite;</emphasis>
Samen 0,2-0,4 mm lang. - 
<normalizedToken id="14DD6A2015C10EB1063BF15AA9DEDEBC" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="829">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="9801951A03CFA151CADC5527D7A5B82A" pageId="null" pageNumber="829">
<emphasis id="C27D970C54AC754D080674D510231896" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="829">Zytologische Angaben. 2n = 22:</emphasis>
Material aus Island (eingeschleppt) (
<normalizedToken id="DEB47143118292F972AB04948DE48549" originalValue="Löve" pageId="null" pageNumber="829">Loeve</normalizedToken>
und 
<normalizedToken id="2BE4EF05A772FF493E9FEB17993825CB" originalValue="Löve" pageId="null" pageNumber="829">Loeve</normalizedToken>
1956b), aus 
<normalizedToken id="93097AD1CD6AC7C225E2477C3CB53B13" originalValue="Großbritannien" pageId="null" pageNumber="829">Grossbritannien</normalizedToken>
und Portugal (Blackburn und Morton 1957).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="1F482CB63E178E598AA33C6D514C2D62" pageId="null" pageNumber="829">
<emphasis id="0E2123ACEF2CBEF560CB8E93A4BC03C2" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="829">Standort.</emphasis>
Kollin. Lockere, oft feuchte, meist kalkarme, sandige 
<normalizedToken id="E6B4D6059C785C7D9B18228EBE9FE01B" originalValue="Böden" pageId="null" pageNumber="829">Boeden</normalizedToken>
in warmen Lagen. Feuchte Rasen, Mauern, 
<normalizedToken id="CAE5A76B128E5FB38F17ECEE7144AB41" originalValue="Wegränder" pageId="null" pageNumber="829">Wegraender</normalizedToken>
, Felsen.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="202BBCF6A1E5F63A2278F50CF50B748D" pageId="null" pageNumber="829">
<emphasis id="C145BA4F88C28C8F9BA0A19BC61428CA" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="829">
Verbreitung. 
<normalizedToken id="253ECCFAEF5371D59E67A45DDD5C2C90" originalValue="Westeuropäische" pageId="null" pageNumber="829">Westeuropaeische</normalizedToken>
Pflanze:
</emphasis>
Westeuropa (nord- und 
<normalizedToken id="4B642D2346BE10AD355F806127981656" originalValue="ostwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="829">ostwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis 
<normalizedToken id="C71D05A1791E2C92C729D4924D843CDF" originalValue="Südnorwegen" pageId="null" pageNumber="829">Suednorwegen</normalizedToken>
, 
<normalizedToken id="F9C686FD5DA64F607E984AA8FA580EBC" originalValue="Südschweden" pageId="null" pageNumber="829">Suedschweden</normalizedToken>
, Schlesien, Karpaten, Westserbien, Albanien). Im Gebiet: Vogesen (Bains), 
<normalizedToken id="640DC3AE516196FBFBC448A7CEA2300A" originalValue="südliches" pageId="null" pageNumber="829">suedliches</normalizedToken>
Tessin, unteres Misox, Comerseegebiet, Veltlin (Morbegno), Bergamasker Alpen (Val Camonica), Vintschgau (Malserheide?); gelegentlich in 
<normalizedToken id="FB60D5E7AA535F521B35497F16C82BAB" originalValue="Gärten" pageId="null" pageNumber="829">Gaerten</normalizedToken>
als Rasenpflanze kultiviert.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
